         <p class="- topic/p ">If battery operation is manually enabled the
rectifier modules output is reduced to simulate that the rectifier
mains is unavailable and to discharge the battery.</p>
         <note type="important" class="- topic/note ">It is not recommended to manually enable battery
operation. It should only be used for service and troubleshooting.</note>
