      <result class="- topic/section task/result ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">The rectifier modules have changed to battery operation
(batterytest). When battery operation is manually enabled the rectifier
modules will <u class="+ topic/ph hi-d/u ">not</u> automatically switch back to float charge.</p>
         <p class="- topic/p ">When the battery voltage has reached the reduced voltage level
of the rectifier modules, the rectifier modules will take over and
supply the load, but the rectifier modules will still indicate that
they are in battery operation. The rectifier modules need to be manually
switched back to float charge.</p>
